Package: gts
Type: Package
Title: Gridded time series data manipulation and analysis
Version: 0.2.9020
Authors@R: 
    person("Ricardo", "Oliveros-Ramos",
           email = "ricardo.oliveros@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8069-2101"))
Description: Management of gridded time-series (arrays with a time dimension),
    with geographical dimensions (longitude, latitude, depth/altitude). The package provides
    methods to read and write gridded time-series (GTS) objects and manage them using
    R time-series methods. 
